  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, you can give yourself vitality when you cheat death or when you help someone else cheat it. You can regain hit points equal to 1d8 + your Constitution modifier (minimum of 1 hit point) when you succeed on a death saving throw or when you stabilize a creature with @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.8zT7njvqbpXs4Cel]{Spare the Dying}.</p>\n<p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p>",
